Short:        TankGL - simple OpenGL Demo
Author:       Marek 'March' Szyprowski <marek@amiga.pl>
Version:      1.0
Architecture: ppc-morphos, x86-win32
Status:       freeware

This is simple OpenGL demo written during Computer Graphics course. The main
goal for this tool was to demonstrate the motion of tank's tracks.

Keyboard mappings:

+/- - move the tank forward/backward
arrows - rotate around the tank
esc/q - quit the demo

